$$\eqalign{ & {\rm{Encapsulated\ amounts\ of\ SUT = Total\ amount }} \cr & \,\,\,\ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ {\rm{of\ SUT - amount\ of\ free\ SUT}} \cr} $$
